data.description: Seller has 2.375% ASSUMABLE loan with approx a $220k payoff.  Gorgeous 3 bed/2 bath with a 3 Car Garage and Community Pool, Spa & Recreation Center. Beautiful  kitchen with espresso cabinets, granite counters, island, stainless steel and pendant lights. Open floor plan with huge family room off the kitchen in addition. Oversized primary bedroom with walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom. Master bath has dual sinks, extra linen storage, private toilet and walk-in shower. Large covered back patio.  Great sized back yard with low maintenance landscaping.
